flowchart TD
    Intake["New Project intake"]
    LocalValidation["Generated project validation"]
    GitHub["GitHub repo and branch published"]
    Cloudflare["Cloudflare preview apply"]
    D1["D1 migrations and preview data scope"]
    WebSmoke["Web preview and API smoke tests"]
    Android["Android preview APK release"]
    Bridge["Bridge installable-app registration"]
    Ready["Initial Preview Release ready"]
    Blocked["Blocked with exact next step"]

    Intake --> LocalValidation
    LocalValidation --> GitHub
    GitHub --> Cloudflare
    Cloudflare --> D1
    D1 --> WebSmoke
    WebSmoke --> Android
    Android --> Bridge
    Bridge --> Ready

    LocalValidation -. missing validation .-> Blocked
    GitHub -. missing GitHub auth .-> Blocked
    Cloudflare -. apply disabled or missing config .-> Blocked
    D1 -. migration failure .-> Blocked
    WebSmoke -. health or URL smoke failure .-> Blocked
    Android -. missing APK asset .-> Blocked
    Bridge -. missing URL or token .-> Blocked
